      <p>This reminds me so much of a soup my Spanish grandmother used to make, with ham, kidney beans and kale. I loved it. She also would make a variation where she rendered the fat from cured chorizo, which added some spice. In any case, I will never grow bored of soup and am glad to see I&#39;m not alone. Happy Thanksgiving.</p>
